cff-version: 1.2.0
title: Little ISMS Helper
message: >-
  If you use this software in academic, audit, or compliance work,
  please cite it using the metadata below.
type: software
authors:
  - alias: moag1000 / moag2000
    website: https://github.com/moag1000
repository-code: https://github.com/moag1000/Little-ISMS-Helper
url: https://github.com/moag1000/Little-ISMS-Helper
abstract: >-
  Open-source multi-tenant Information Security Management System (ISMS)
  with multi-framework compliance support for ISO 27001:2022,
  BSI IT-Grundschutz, NIS-2 (EU 2022/2555), DORA (EU 2022/2554),
  GDPR/DSGVO, and TISAX. Implements all 93 ISO 27001 Annex A controls,
  a quantitative risk engine (5x5 matrix with risk-appetite gating),
  cross-framework mapping, GDPR data-subject-request workflows,
  data-breach notification (Art. 33 / 72h), DPIA, and a
  tamper-evident audit trail with HMAC-SHA256 chaining.
keywords:
  - isms
  - iso-27001
  - bsi-grundschutz
  - nis2
  - dora
  - gdpr
  - dsgvo
  - tisax
  - compliance
  - grc
  - information-security
  - risk-management
  - audit-trail
  - multi-tenant
  - symfony
